Who's that there? Is that Mike?
That's Mike. Oh, wow!

19:21.615 --> 19:24.134
This is after George had died?

19:24.135 --> 19:27.574
I would think so, otherwise...
And which one is Liz now?

19:27.575 --> 19:32.373
The one standing up? Yeah.
