between the two deaths they've had
Ratliff's body exhumed

38:12.842 --> 38:14.640
from the cemetery here in Texas

38:14.641 --> 38:18.641
and brought to the medical
examiner's office in Chapel Hill.

38:25.720 --> 38:29.678
A little water in there.
