40:54.857 --> 40:57.415
I really didn't know
who Michael Peterson was,

40:57.416 --> 40:58.975
other than being a writer.

40:58.976 --> 41:01.376
Um...

41:02.375 --> 41:03.974
..and a military veteran.

41:03.975 --> 41:08.774
I didn't know him personally.
