Anyway, I'm very optimistic

42:13.285 --> 42:17.523
about what our findings
are going to be, Wednesday.

42:17.524 --> 42:22.322
That was Elizabeth's sister,
Margaret Blair.

42:22.323 --> 42:23.603
She lives in Rhode Island.

43:31.952 --> 43:33.752
I expect him to be found guilty...

